---
description: Best practices for Next.js applications and routing
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use the App Router for better performance and improved data fetching.
- Implement proper error boundaries to handle runtime errors gracefully.
- Utilize Next.js built-in optimizations like Image and Script components.
- Leverage Incremental Static Regeneration (ISR) for dynamic content.